tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    training_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    feedback_rating INT,
    feedback_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE model_performance (
    performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    precision_score FLOAT,
    recall_score FLOAT,
    f1_score FLOAT
);
